{"tid":2175163,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"借問聲 上連登上到比時事台stalker 24小時mon po滋擾有何良策？","createTime":"2020-08-26T10:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T10:44:48.000Z","uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f4d32789bfed980ef70cd272fe6d0d4506037cc7","tid":2175163,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"借問聲 上連登上到比時事台stalker 24小時mon po滋擾有何良策？<br />\n<br />\n其實我本身就唔介意既，諗住block左就算，不過問題係每次我開新post佢就秒入然後copy n paste，跟住就會變成完全冇人再針對我post主題黎回應。 而且我既新post一、既唔係時事台 二、同政治完全無關，上得連登 尤其是感情台呢d台 都係想放鬆下擺低下心事姐，點解乜都要被政治綁架呢？ <br />\n而且講還講點解要因為人地係lgbt就鬧人死變態呢？莫非我lgbt會比起你24小時mon住我post stalk住我黎滋擾更變態嗎？<br />\n如果咁唔喜歡我既話，我可以永遠唔再入時事台 唔會再係時事台任何既post發表任何意見，請問咁樣滿唔滿意？可唔可以唔好再24小時跟蹤我？其實個感覺真係好噁心<br />\n<br />\n我原本係完全封鎖，岩岩解返cap圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每次出新post一分鐘內必到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPB67xX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPB67xX.jpg&h=16f65539&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvpksxX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvpksxX.jpg&h=72d21ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g5v7RZD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg5v7RZD.jpg&h=9b94e40c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxFr7xZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxFr7xZ.jpg&h=8b2d94cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOxiecZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOxiecZ.jpg&h=ea5e1841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想呼籲下呢位人士，一個好簡單既要求，請問你可唔可以唔好再跟住我啊？得唔得啊？🙏🏻"},{"pid":"8aef148810ac9cd3e8259287b6f1856e1aabdcd5","tid":2175163,"uid":143343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:33:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41499efc718d34ec8384c082630c4121650df020","tid":2175163,"uid":143343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:33:24.000Z","msg":"